                  </persName>
            . I went to Gerrard-street on the 7th of May, and saw the prisoner with this lamp concealed about him; it had been taken from the shelf in the <placeName id="t18280529-84-crimeloc464">Westminster Dispensary</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280529-84-crimeloc464" type="placeName" value="Westminster Dispensary"></interp>
