                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-84-off460 t18280529-84-crimeloc464"></join> - Sir Peter Laurie is one of the Trustees, and there are several others.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280529-84-person555">
                  MERCY 
                  DAY
               <interp inst="t18280529-84-person555" type="surname" value="DAY"></interp>
